{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_128","type":"agent_message","text":"The mailbox section is the same pattern as routers: Akka reflectively loads an internal requirements map and then mailbox implementations from its own `reference.conf`. I’m adding the full semantics map plus the mailbox-type constructors under a `Mailboxes` condition so we don’t burn more cycles one queue at a time."}}
